Privacy Policy – WhereKept
Effective Date: April 3, 2026
WhereKept ("the App") is designed to help users store and locate household items such as documents, chargers, keys, and other personal belongings.
1. Information We Collect
WhereKept does not require account registration and does not collect personal identity information such as name, email address, or phone number.
The information you enter in the app, including:
item names
room names
storage locations
notes
is stored locally on your device only.
2. Local Data Storage
All saved data remains on your device using local storage technology.We do not upload your saved items to any server or cloud service.
If you uninstall the app, your stored data may be deleted unless backed up by your device system.
3. Advertising
The app may display advertisements provided by Google AdMob.
Ad providers may collect limited device information such as:
device type
advertising ID
approximate location
ad interaction data
This information is managed according to Google's privacy practices.
4. Third-Party Services
The app uses third-party advertising services provided by Google.
Third-party services may process data under their own privacy policies.
5. Data Security
Because all item data is stored locally, control of your saved information remains with you.
6. Children's Privacy
This app is not directed specifically to children under 13, but it does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
7. Changes to This Policy
This Privacy Policy may be updated when app features change.
8. Contact
For privacy-related questions, users may contact the app developer through the contact information provided on the app listing.
